<p>That's precisely what I'm saying is wrong with the scenario - that they just <em>assume</em> it's supernatural because it does something a little odd as opposed to first ruling out rational explanations. The Foundation is composed of scientists, not tinfoil hatters who want to believe. Granted, there would surely be a few among their ranks, but they would be in the minority.</p>
